# VigiNote OSINT Alerts Bot

Posts high-severity OSINT alerts (conflict, political instability, disasters, outbreaks) to a Telegram channel with:
- Headline, 2-sentence dek, bullets, source link
- Cross-source de-dup (max 2 outlets per story / 24h)
- Region coverage + per-region minimums
- Daily & per-run caps, min gap, quiet hours
- AI bullet summaries if `OPENAI_API_KEY` is set; extractive fallback otherwise

## Quick start (local)
```bash
python3 -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
cp .env.example .env  # fill in TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN & TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID etc.
python main.py
